mixin typography(heading, text)
    div(class="typo-container typo-container_first")
        .typo-container__heading-container
            h1(class="typo-container__heading") H1
        .typo-container__text-container
            h1.typo-container__text This one is the sub-section or widget title
    div(class="typo-container typo-container_second")
        .typo-container__heading-container 
            h2(class="typo-container__heading") H2
        .typo-container__text-container
            h2.typo-container__text Next one is the item title inside widgets
    div(class="typo-container typo-container_third")
        .typo-container__heading-container 
            h3(class="typo-container__heading") H3
        .typo-container__text-container
            h3.typo-container__text This is a label or CTA text
    div(class="typo-container")
        .typo-container__heading-container
            p(class="typo-container__heading") Body
        .typo-container__text-container
            p.typo-container__text This is the body text which is used for most of the design, like paragraphs, lists, etc.

    